[14:09:17.031] [INFO ]   Q: What is the annual L&D budget per employee and how does it work?
[14:09:17.031] [INFO ] ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
