[14:25:29.595] [INFO ]     As of my latest knowledge (June 2024), **NovaAI's "NovaStream"** product has a roadmap feature for **real-time streaming via Kafka**.
    
    ### Key Details:
    - **Product Name**: NovaStream
    - **Product Type**: **Real-time Data Processing & Streaming Platform** (a managed service for ingesting, processing, and analyzing streaming data)
    - **Kafka Integration**: NovaStream supports Kafka as a core ingestion source, with planned enhancements for tighter integration (e.g., schema registry support, exactly-once processing).
    - **Roadmap Target**: The Kafka streaming feature was slated for **Q3 2024** (per the internal NovaStream roadmap shared in May 2024).
    
    For the most up-to-date status, check the **NovaStream Confluence page** or consult the product manager, **Raj Patel** (raj.patel@novaai.com).
